ActSustaining Canada's Economic Recovery Act
Jobs and Economic Growth Act
SubjectOrder Fixing April 1, 2015 as the Day on which Certain Provisions of the Acts Come into Force
PrecisOrder (1) fixing April 1, 2015 as the day on which section 1804 and subsection 1820(6) of the JOBS AND ECONOMIC GROWTH ACT, chapter 12 of the Statutes of Canada, 2010, COME INTO FORCE; and (2) fixing April 1, 2015, as the day on which section 183, subsection 192(1), section 195 and subsection 196(3) of the SUSTAINING CANADA'S ECONOMIC RECOVERY ACT, chapter 25 of the Statutes of Canada, 2010, COME INTO FORCE.
